# Garden Gantt — local environment overrides (Vite reads .env.local)
# Copy this file to .env.local and edit. .env.local is gitignored.

# === Permapeople integration (Phase 2 / CAT-06) ===
#
# In production: leave default; the build will use the same-origin Worker proxy
# (see cors-proxy/README.md for deployment).
# In dev: point at wrangler dev local Worker, OR direct to permapeople.org with
# API keys. CORS will fail in production with direct mode (see 02-CORS-SPIKE.md).
VITE_PERMAPEOPLE_BASE_URL=/permapeople-proxy

# Direct mode (DEV ONLY — requires CORS-friendly origin, e.g. browser proxy or
# wrangler dev). Production deployments MUST NOT set these — keys would be baked
# into the public bundle. The Worker holds these server-side via wrangler secret.
# VITE_PERMAPEOPLE_BASE_URL=https://garden-gantt-permapeople-proxy.YOUR-USER.workers.dev
# VITE_PERMAPEOPLE_KEY_ID=...
# VITE_PERMAPEOPLE_KEY_SECRET=...
